lexUnit.name: incomparable.a
lexUnit.definition: COD: without an equal in quality or extent; matchless

sentence.text: The many shops and bars at this exceptionally pretty little resort are close to the hotel , which features a large sun terrace where drinks can be enjoyed against the backdrop of the incomparable beauty of Lake Garda .
